Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Entertainment District?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, that thing!\NKnow what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The place where...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am a god!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You three are...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first thing\Nyou need to pound into your heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drive it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're to turn into dogs if I tell you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arf, arf, arf, arf!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Turn into monkeys if I say so!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hunch over and rub your hands together,\Nconstantly pander to my every whim
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and suck up to me\Nwith every fiber of your being!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's our Lord Uzui all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And let me repeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I am a god!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy is crazy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:00:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you the god of, specifically?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't believe this guy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good question!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have potential!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's a stupid question!\NWhat potential?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The God of Flashiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.92,0:01:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the God of Festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What an idiot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's the God of Stupidity.\NNo question about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the King of the Mountains!\NNice to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,God of Festivals!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}No! You two are a close match\Nfor each other! Cringeworthy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Back off, Inosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let me go, Konpochiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, he only has distaste for those\Nliving in the same dimension.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, there's no time to fool around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He vanished?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So fast! Look how far he's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's no bigger than a sesame seed now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is the power\Nof the God of Festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, that man is Tengen Uzui, a Hashira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go after him!\NGo after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Safe travels!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}EPISODE 2:\NINFILTRATING THE ENTERTAINMENT DISTRICT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything\Nthat'll make you stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that we're only here\Nto case the joint.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you do,\Ndon't get out of the carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't do it, Zenitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those stinking brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Settle down, Inosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yellow Boy! Stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's daytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is the Yoshiwara Entertainment District.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Awash in vanity\Nand desire of men and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A town of the night\Nswirling with love and hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Flashy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's teeming with people!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Comin' through!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the... Calm down, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}DESTROY
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where did the kid\Nwith the yellow head go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You there, Yellow Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stop by?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This place is full of beautiful ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're too young for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See, this place goes to sleep during the day,\Nand at night, it sparkles and dazzles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The ideal place for a demon, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Women who become Courtesans\Nare mostly sold here due to poverty and debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In return, they're given food,\Nclothing and lodging,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and if they can climb up the ranks,\Na rich man might buy out their contracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are ranks among Courtesans, as well.\NThe highest-ranked "Oiran" is on a different level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beauty is a given, and she's also intelligent\Nand has mastered every traditional art.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's the breadwinner, on whom\Neach house has lavished time and money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A woman of distinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}All right, that's enough scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.43,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WISTERIA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sorry to impose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you've infiltrated the Entertainment\NDistrict, first look for my bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be digging for information\Non the demons, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll thank you not to mess with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you use your subordinates\Nto personally find a bride for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How did you get that idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! I'm going to have my say!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zenitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that a screwed-up oddball like you\Nhas no luck with the ladies! However! Even so!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you want a wife,\Nthat's no reason to use Demon Slayers like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Are you an idiot? I'm talking about a wife\Nwho's infiltrated the Entertainment District
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and is hard at work\Ngathering intel on the demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've stopped receiving regular check-ins,\Nso I'm going, too, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose that's what you fantasize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You damn punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are the letters\Nsent via the Kasugai Crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's quite a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Has she been undercover\Nfor a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do have three of them. Wives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wives?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Th-Three? Why, you... Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why would you have three of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, in the letters, they keep reminding you\Nnot to stand out when you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I told you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are we going to do, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well, of course, disguise yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}As much as I hate it, in a drab way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All three of my wives\Nare brilliant ninjas. Kunoichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure that this district would be\Nthe perfect place for the demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but when I went in as a customer,\NI couldn't get anything on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I sent them in\Nto get closer than a customer ever could.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since I've already narrowed down\Nthe likeliest houses to three,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you three will search for my wives there\Nand gather information.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Suma of the Tokito House,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Makio of the Ogimoto House,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and Hinatsuru of the Kyogoku House.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your wives must be dead,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have brought you\Nthe items you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}DEMON SLAYER: KIMETSU NO YAIBA\NENTERTAINMENT DISTRICT ARC
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}DEMON SLAYER: KIMETSU NO YAIBA\NENTERTAINMENT DISTRICT ARC
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, my... Now these three are certainly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}quite homely girls, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}INOKO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SUMIKO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}ZENKO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there any way you can reconsider?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Under your training, Madam,\NI'm sure they'd turn into diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess taking in one\Nwouldn't be a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to impose, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I think we'll take\Nthe one in the middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She looks very obedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to work as hard as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SUMIKO: EMPLOYED
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are beyond hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can barely give you away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking to you, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you incensed because I made you\Ndisguise yourself as a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd do anything I asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't give a damn\Nabout dressing like a girl, moron!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's that face of yours!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at you! You're a stud!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't screw with me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Over there!\NA bunch of people are swarming around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a procession of Courtesans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's Tokito House's Koinatsu Oiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The highest-ranking Courtesan\Nis going off to meet her client.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How flashy is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wife? Is she your wife, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Is that knockout your wife?\NThat's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You've got three of them!\NAre they all beautiful like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She's not my wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She walks so slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She'd get killed in a second\Nin the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking this girl\Nback to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Ogimoto House chaperone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she's caught the eye of the Ogimoto House,\NI couldn't be more thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But what kind of stroke of luck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please, I have a sure eye\Nfor these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of yourself, Inoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,INOKO: EMPLOYED
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh no! I'm the only leftover!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,REJECTED
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}OGIMOTO HOUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my! Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:13:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They'd plastered her face in a bizarre way,\Nbut just look at her now that it's off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a steal!\NBuying such a beauty so cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll train her like nobody's business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure she's in more demand than Kyogoku\NHouse's Warabihime or Tokito House's Koinatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but this girl is actually quite sturdy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's better for a girl\Nto be plump and meaty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's more muscular than plump.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:35.25,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KYOGOKU HOUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that girl can\Nreally play the shamisen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she's so dynamic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did she join us recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to have a good ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that she can play the shamisen\Nor koto after just one listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she sure is ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised that she got taken in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The man who brought her here\Nwas drop-dead gorgeous, I hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my! Was he really?\NI wish I could've seen him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that chaperone hag\Nwas totally smitten!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know what? I can tell.\NThat girl is to rise to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The grittiness to get back at the man\Nwho abandoned her... I can sense it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A girl like that has a backbone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}You can have her clean the toilets or whatever!\NPlease, just take her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Heck, I'd even give her away for free if I had to!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to make that guy pay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I swear I'm going to become\Nthe number one Oiran in Yoshiwara!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}TOKITO HOUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sumiko? Sumiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're so short-staffed now.\NCould you carry these up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!\NI'll take them up right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! You're such a hard worker!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}After we removed your makeup,\Nshe found the scar on your forehead,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}so the madam was seething\Nwith rage yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Just stop it! It's no use\Nlashing out at this poor child!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'm so glad\Nthey're letting me work here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she rather strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're saying that Kyogoku House's madam\Nfell from a window and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's scary. Let's be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of the older girls are leaving\Nthese days, committing Ashinuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's Ashinuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot of baggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're all gifts for Koinatsu Oiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sumiko, you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ashinuke means to run away from here\Nwithout paying off your debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's really bad if you get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Some people do manage\Nto run off with the man they love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, like the other day, Suma Oiran...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Suma?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}That's Uzui's wife.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop spreading those rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, nobody knows\Nif she really did make it out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Right.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, you brought\Nthese up for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give you some candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eat it in secret by yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want some, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oiran! Oiran!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. You just had some, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, did Suma Oiran commit Ashinuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you ask a question like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She has her guard up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to find a way\Nto ask about Miss Suma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Suma Oiran is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,older sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TANJIRO IS SO HONEST THAT HE CAN'T ASSUME\NA NORMAL EXPRESSION WHEN HE LIES
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you were sold into the Entertainment\NDistrict after your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been exchanging letters\Nwith my sister all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I know she wouldn't commit Ashinuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True, I couldn't believe\Nthat Suma would commit Ashinuke, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was such a grounded girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There were no signs\Nthat she was infatuated with any man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But they found her diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I hear that she'd written\Nabout committing Ashinuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ashinuke...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How convenient is that for demons?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if someone were to vanish,\Npeople would only assume that she'd run away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The diary was probably forged.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I pray that you're safe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}We're going to rescue you,\Nno matter what, Miss Suma!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}All quiet today, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I'm getting a really bad feeling.\NIt's like being enveloped in smoke.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}So adept at becoming invisible...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Could it be that the demon residing here\Nis an Upper Rank demon?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}If that's the case...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we could be in\Nfor an ultra-flashy fight to the death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So hot! I'm dying to take these off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wearing this stupid outfit\Nblunts my senses like you wouldn't believe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yae! Do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Makio's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's shut herself into her room\Nand won't come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and all she said is that she wasn't feeling well,\Nbut she won't go the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sooner or later,\Nthe madam's going to drag her out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just brought a meal to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I only left it outside her door, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Makio? That's Uzui's wife.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally heard her name mentioned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not feeling well?\NLike that would stop her from checking in?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That woman came\Nfrom that direction, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guess I'll take a look.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Inoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll hurt yourself if you rush like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a quiet girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have a husky voice,\Nso don't ever say a word!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you stink at falsetto, so everyone will know\Nright away that you're a guy. I'm not kidding.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}What am I supposed to do, dammit?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who were you writing these letters to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. It's Makio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Makio.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.98,0:23:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}NIN-NIN
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.94,0:23:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-nin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It kills me to admit it,\Nbut you're a stunner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's time for a Taisho-era secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In spite of himself, Zenitsu seems\Nto have taken a shine to the shamisen,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and he's become\Nquite a skilled player! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm scared to be alone in the house,\Nso is it okay if I come over?
